          "settings": {
            "enlarge_text": true,
            "text": "<p>The WoodWork Collective Distilling Company was founded on a single conviction: that great spirits are not manufactured into existence, but carefully revealed. We are a whiskey house devoted to the art of selection, blending, secondary maturation, and finishing—with a particular emphasis on how wood, time, and judgment can elevate an already excellent distillate into something rarer, more expressive, and more complete.</p>"
