            "image_mask": "none",
            "image_width": 650,
            "title": "Cask Selection",
            "text": "<p>We seek out exceptional barrels and distillates, then pair them with complementary cooperage and aging environments to draw out their best qualities. Oak is not treated as a blunt instrument—it is treated as a fine material with its own personality, capable of shaping whiskey in subtle and profound ways when used with discipline and intelligence.</p>",
