            "image": "shopify://shop_images/prettyAltschuler.jpg",
            "image_mask": "square",
            "image_width": 650,
            "title": "The Craft of Maturation",
            "text": "<p>Our work is not merely about finishing in the superficial sense. We treat wood as an active creative medium: a structural force that can deepen texture, frame aroma, refine the palate, and bring latent character into focus. Every cask choice, every transfer, every month of secondary aging is meant to serve the whiskey rather than overpower it.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": ""
