            "image_width": 650,
            "title": "The Collective",
            "text": "<p>The word Collective is intentional. Our work is collaborative by design, drawing on the insights of blenders, reviewers, enthusiasts, and specialized partners. This is not whiskey made by committee—it is whiskey refined through a circle of informed taste, shaped by expertise, conversation, and the shared pursuit of excellence.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
